      Y ou are allowed to perform right shif t operation any number of times.   One right shift operation m ea ns shifting all elements of  the array by one
   position intheri ght direct ion. The la st element o f thearray will be moved to
   the  starting position in the ar ray i.e. 0th in dex.
    If itis possible to o btai n the sorted array by performing the above oper ation    then re t urntrue else return False.
